42902a5e-d870-48b3-a89c-3a8f262a1c7c/661-1
00:04:21.437 --> 00:04:22.986
<v Lina Čeponienė>nors gerai arba blogai pasako.</v>

42902a5e-d870-48b3-a89c-3a8f262a1c7c/664-0
00:04:24.096 --> 00:04:25.016
<v Lina Čeponienė>O, kodėl ne?</v>

42902a5e-d870-48b3-a89c-3a8f262a1c7c/749-0
